      <ownedComment xmi:id="4a4df041-cc77-421d-a589-b4323512ff28" body="The {xor} constraint is applied to a set of associations, specifying that&#xA;over that set, exactly one is manifest for each associated instance. Xor is&#xA;an exclusive or (not inclusive or) constraint." annotatedElement="7f6e5860-cfc9-4577-b2ac-84d446f4ec19">
